databaseQueries.query: SELECT "users".*, (SELECT count(*) FROM "workspaces" inner join "user_workspace" on "workspaces"."id" = "user_workspace"."workspace_id" WHERE "users"."id" = "user_workspace"."user_id") as "workspaces_count" FROM "users" WHERE "id" = '53' LIMIT 1

SELECT * FROM "subscriptions" WHERE "subscriptions"."user_id" = 53 and "subscriptions"."user_id" IS not NULL ORDER BY "created_at" DESC
